title: Moebius - I am not Batman (1995) [CBR]
description:
Moebius - I am not Batman (1995) [CBR]

This is Moebius's take on the legendary DC figure. DC refused to publish it. I wonder why...


A side note from the magazine:
 "[...] the story he created for this book, "I AM NOT BATMAN" (BATMAN is (c) & (R) 1995 DC Comics and BATMAN is not in this magazine.), was first presented, in a completely different form, to DC Comics, who rejected it as too controversial and refused to pay him for his work."
